{"tid":985992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【順豐審查】為拒寄十字架道歉 炒港區總經理「祭旗」","createTime":"2019-01-18T06:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T14:24:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"22483e510f555bf65059f5bc7a8e795db159a765","tid":985992,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190118/large/1547790448_a37e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190118%2Flarge%2F1547790448_a37e.png&h=9c5e91c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順豐速運近日接連爆發拒寄書籍和十字架事件，令人質疑有政治審查。順豐集團今日發聲明指，集團決定香港順豐的總經理立刻引咎辭職，並向所涉當事人和受到困擾的社會各界人士表示深切的歉意。聲明將拒寄責任歸咎於香港管理層未能充分理解目的地的海關法律，疏於對工作人員進行培訓，造成前線員工執行過度和矯枉過正。<br />\n<br />\n順豐在聲明回應拒寄十字架事件，指工作人員目測該物件屬於宗教物品，即錯誤判斷為禁寄品而拒絕收件。集團其後組成調查小組，發現香港順豐服務範圍內確實存在類似問題。聲明承認，事件絕對違背集團以客戶為中心的經營理念，又強調絕對不應忘本，對此事件感到不能理解和十分震驚。順豐集團指，會儘快針對調查所發現的情況，檢討現時管理機制出現的問題並作完善，杜絕類似事件再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190118/59156716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190118%2F59156716&d=QL8Dn08IhbOMzyUdcig6xdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4938900e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190118%2F59156716&h=fcf02a3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190118/59156716</a>"},{"pid":"e10157e1882d65d6d702623187be8881adebad44","tid":985992,"uid":28970,"like":35,"dislike":6,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗"},{"pid":"68abd56248f7bd39ebf8431bc658471a52d3278b","tid":985992,"uid":59617,"like":165,"dislike":2,"score":163,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"關個gm差事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f66c964ad13ff443f9344ecc8fcd654cfbc259",